ProjectsArray.Title: QUEEN OF TEARS
ProjectsArray.About: Queen of Tears is an ongoing South Korean television series written by Park Ji-eun, co-directed by Jang Young-woo and Kim Hee-won, and starring Kim Soo-hyun and Kim Ji-won. The series depicts the story of a married couple in a crisis. It premiered on tvN on March 9, 2024, and airs every Saturday and Sunday at 21:10 (KST). It is also available for streaming on TVING in South Korea, and on Netflix in selected regions.
